           This sample showcases the clipboard operation capabilities of SfDataGrid. The SfDataGrid, provides an interactive support to perform cut, copy and paste operations by using GridCopyOption and GridPasteOption properties. The GridCopyOption provides options like None, CopyData, CutData, IncludeHeaders, and IncludeFormat and the GridPasteOption provides options like None, PasteData, IncludeFirstLine.


